212
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:55,120
Da sam na vašem mestu, dobro
bih pazio šta radim.

213
00:25:56,040 --> 00:26:01,280
Naredniče Kediros, pravac kuhinja!
-Kapetane! Kapetane!

214
00:26:46,760 --> 00:26:48,800
Dodaj malo vitamina!

215
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:56,633
Jagnjetina ili piletina?
Jagnjetina.

216
00:26:56,800 --> 00:27:01,720
